        "multi-agent",
        "cognitive architecture"
      ],
      "score": 0.95,
      "hebbian_credit": 10,
      "layer": "L8",
      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.ma.new5",
      "snippet": "Proposes NOMA query optimization framework for multi-agent data pipelines addressing multidimensional search space, variable topologies, and no common operator algebra. Experiments show extreme variance: 153x cost, 5x latency, 25% quality. Optimal planning is heterogeneous. Integrated optimization loop: plan generation, cost estimation, runtime refinement, semantic caching."
    },
    {
      "id": "sparse-sensor-placement-in-multi-agent-rl-control-",
      "name": "Sparse Sensor Placement in Multi-Agent RL Control of Rayleigh-Benard Convection",
      "dir": "sparse-sensor-placement-in-multi-agent-rl-control-/",
      "source": "arXiv:cs.MA:2607.new",
