      "score": 0.95,
      "hebbian_credit": 10,
      "layer": "L8",
      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.ma.new4",
      "snippet": "Sparse sensor placement via distilled sparse apprenticeship policies for fluid dynamic control. Multi-Agent Transformer policy outperforms PPO in stability. Sparse apprenticeship retains dense expert control behavior. Grouped regularization achieves near-maximal sparsity, reducing per-agent observations from 360 to 12, decreasing data throughput."
    },
    {
