      "snippet": "FlashPrefill from WeChat/CAS automates the prefill stage of long-context LLM inference by discovering attention patterns and dynamic thresholding with near-zero cost, completely clipping attention long-tail and using index compression for physical skipping. At 256K context, FlashPrefill achieves 27.78x operator acceleration. This addresses the key bottleneck where prefill time grows quadratically with context length, making it the true user-experience bottleneck for long-context scenarios."
