      "layer": "L8",
      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.04291",
      "snippet": "Multi-expert systems where multiple LLMs collaborate are increasingly adopted. However orchestration policies governing expert interaction remain largely opaque. We disentangle intrinsic importance from emergent structure in multi-expert orchestration."
    },
    {
      "id": "arxiv-2607.10811",
