      "layer": "L8",
      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.09714",
      "snippet": "The Feedback-Coupled Memory Systems (FCMS) architecture formalizes closed-loop coordination through four abstract operators. The FCMS framework proposes a formal approach to memory-system coupling through continuous-time dynamics, relevant to cognitive architecture design in agentic systems."
    },
    {
      "id": "arxiv-2607.11787",
