      "hebbian_credit": 8,
      "layer": "L8",
      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.11787",
      "snippet": "Shared meaning in language requires people to learn and agree on categories. We ask how characteristics of agents memories change the emergence and evolution of shared meaning in groups without partnership payoffs."
    },
    {
      "id": "arxiv-2607.09842",
