      "url": "https://arxiv.org/abs/2607.09691",
      "snippet": "A modern coding agent can hold an entire repository in its context window. Most of its reading is wasted. We study what context the agent actually needs when it must edit code. Separating finding the work site from acting on it we vary code representation and score against SWE-bench."
